OL,3,CWhy do the clocks go forward and what
OL,4,Cimpact does it have on your health?
OL,6,FBritish Summer Time (BST) officially
OL,7,Fstarts on Sunday when the clocks go
OL,8,Fforward one hour.
OL,10,FIt marks the end of Greenwich Mean
OL,11,FTime (GMT) and will mean longer spells
OL,12,Fof daylight into evenings.
OL,14,FIt may seem like a minor adjustment,
OL,15,Fbut it could have a bigger impact on
OL,16,Fhealth than one might think.
OL,18,FITV News explains what you need to
OL,19,Fknow about why and when the clocks go
OL,20,Fforward, as well as the impact on your
OL,21,Fbody.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
