OL,3,CWhy do the clocks go forward and what
OL,4,Cimpact does it have on your health?
OL,6,FWhen do the clocks go forward?
OL,8,FThe clocks go forward at 1am on the
OL,9,Flast Sunday in March. This year, it
OL,10,Fwill be on March 29.
OL,12,FBST, or daylight saving time (DST),
OL,13,Flasts until the final Sunday of
OL,14,FOctober, when the clocks go back an
OL,15,Fhour.
OL,17,FWhen was daylight savings introduced?
OL,19,FDespite popular theories, daylight
OL,20,Fsavings was not introduced to help
OL,21,Ffarmers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
