OL,3,CWhy do the clocks go forward and what
OL,4,Cimpact does it have on your health?
OL,6,FHe died before any law was implemented
OL,7,Fin the UK, but his great-great-
OL,8,Fgrandson, Coldplay singer Chris
OL,9,FMartin, has seen it in action.
OL,11,FThe first country to adopt daylight
OL,12,Fsavings was Germany in 1916, during
OL,13,Fthe First World War. The UK followed
OL,14,Fsuit a few weeks later.
