OL,3,CWhy do the clocks go forward and what
OL,4,Cimpact does it have on your health?
OL,6,FWhat are the benefits of daylight
OL,7,Fsaving time?
OL,9,FExtended evening daylight has many
OL,10,Fbenefits, and not just in improving
OL,11,Fpeople's mood in the lighter evenings.
OL,13,FDaylight savings has been shown to
OL,14,Freduce crime due to increased
OL,15,Fvisibility in the evening, boost the
OL,16,Feconomy as people engage in outdoor
OL,17,Factivities for longer, and decrease
OL,18,Fenergy consumption.
OL,20,FHow does the time change impact your
OL,21,Fhealth?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
