PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1774696008
OL,3,CWhy do the clocks go forward and what
OL,4,Cimpact does it have on your health?
OL,6,FYouGov published a poll in October
OL,7,Fshowing that if our current system
OL,8,Fwere axed, 59% of Britons would opt
OL,9,Ffor the country to stay permanently on
OL,10,FBST.
OL,12,FDr O'Neill argued that the clock
OL,13,Fchanges should be stopped.
OL,15,FHe said: "I'm sure it was extremely
OL,16,Fuseful for our forebears 100 years
OL,17,Fago, but there is quite a strong
OL,18,Fargument for just having permanent
OL,19,Fdaylight saving these days."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
